quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  6,102,yahi ( Awsaf rakhnay wala ) khuda tumhara perwar-digaar hai. is ke siwa koi mabood nahi. ( wohi ) har cheez ka paida karnay wala ( hai ) to isi ki ibadat karo. aur woh har cheez ka nigaran hai
  6,103,( woh aisa hai ke ) nigehain is ka idraak nahi krsktin aur woh nigahon ka idraak karsaktha hai aur woh bhaid jan-nay wala khabardaar hai
  6,104,( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam! un se keh do ke ) tumahray ( paas ) perwar-digaar ki taraf se ( roshan ) daleelen poanch chuki hain to jis ne ( un ko aankhh khol kar ) dekha is ne apna bhalakiya aur jo andha bana raha is ne apne haq mein burakiya. aur mein tumhara nigehbaan nahi hon
  6,105,aur hum isi terhan apni ayatain phair phair kar bayan karte hain taakay kafir yeh nah kahin ke tum ( yeh baatein ahal kitaab se ) sekhe hue ho aur taakay samajhney walay logon ke liye tashreeh kar dein
  6,106,aur jo hukum tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se tumahray paas aata hai isi ki pairwi karo. is ( perwar-digaar ) ke siwa koi mabood nahi. aur mushrikon se kinara karlo
  6,107,aur agar khuda chahta to yeh log shirk nah karte. aur ( ae paighambar! ) hum ne tum ko un par nigehbaan muqarrar nahikiya. aur nah tum un ke Darogha ho
  6,108,aur jin logon ko yeh mushriq khuda ke siwa pkarte hain un ko bura nah kehna ke yeh bhi kahin khuda ko be adbi se be samjhay bura ( nah ) keh bathain. is terhan hum ne har aik firqay ke aamaal ( un ki nazron mein ) achay kar dukhaay hain. phir un ko apne perwar-digaar kaaf taraf lout kar jana hai tab woh un ko betaye ga ke wohkiyakiya karte they
  6,109,aur yeh log khuda ki sakht sakht kasmain khatay hain ke agar un ke paas koi nishani aeye to woh is par zurori imaan le ayen. keh do ke nishanain to sab khuda hi ke paas hain. aur ( momino! ) tumhekiya maloom hai ( yeh to aisay badbakht hain ke un ke paas ) nishanain aa bhi jayen tab bhi imaan nah layein
  6,110,aur hum un ke dilon aur aankhon ko ulat den ge ( to ) jaisay yeh is ( quran ) par pehli dafaa imaan nahi laaye ( waisay phir nah layein ge ) aur un ko chore den ge ke apni sar kashi mein behektey rahen
